channel.title: Am I just being paranoid? READ ALL OF IT!
channel.description:
Last night I had a dream, it started out showing an FBI van driving fast down a highway, then it pulled in to my driveway. Suddenly, 3 FBI agents opened the side-slide door to the van. I was in my room on the computer working on my RuneScape Private Server and they came jumping in through my window, breaking the glass. I quickly got up and ran out of my room in an attempted escape even though I didn't know why they were at my house. One FBI agent had this little object in his hand, it was like three black nerf darts taped together but without the rubber cup on the front of it. He threw it right next to me and it tazed me and I was on the ground wiggling around trying to break free of this invisible net on me. The picked me up and were putting handcuffs on me but that's when I woke up.
Today, I was really worried and I've been thinking lately that the FBI's out to get me. Do you think this dream was a sign to stop with rsps or I'll get arrested? Or it was just a dream and it won't happen? I know this sounds insane but that dream has been bugging me a lot lately.
